[[File:Burnt bones detail.png|left|150px]]
'''Burnt bones''' are one of the few bones that [[free players]] can bury to train Prayer, with the others being [[monkey bones]], [[bones|normal bones]] and [[big bones]]. They can be found in the [[Kebos Battlefront]], the [[Lizardman Canyon]], and various locations in the [[Wilderness]].

Burnt bones give 4.5 Prayer experience when buried. This can be increased by offering the bones in different ways: 
* 13.5 XP when casting [[Sinister Offering]].
* 13.5 XP when offered at the [[Sacred Bone Burner]] after the appropriate faith level has been achieved.
* 15.7 XP when offered at a [[gilded altar]] with two burners lit or at the [[Chaos Temple (hut)|Chaos Temple]].
* 18 XP when offered at the [[Ectofuntus]] in the form of [[burnt bonemeal]].

It is not recommended to train prayer with burnt bones, as they are no different from regular [[bones]], which are much easier to obtain.

